|dead-url=no
}}</ref>2006年有教友696,000人，佔總人口90.0%。有七十個堂區、司鐸185人。現任教區主教為{{link-pt|若瑟·吉斯隆|José Gislon}}<ref name="Vatican20190626">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 26.06.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/06/26/190626b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821145704/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/06/26/190626b.html |archivedate=2019-08-21 |language=en |date=2019-06-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-pt|內·保祿·莫雷托|Nei Paulo Moretto}}和{{link-en|亞歷山大·加爾默羅·魯菲諾尼|Alessandro Carmelo Ruffinoni}}<ref name="Vatican20190626" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 06.07.2011 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/07/06/0425/01064.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821170808/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/07/06/0425/01064.html |archivedate=2019-08-21 |language=it |date=2011-07-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

